#: src/providers/routing.md
msgid "**Per-call backend selection** — \"use the cheap model unless this prompt looks like reasoning.\" Each routing target is its own `[agents.<alias>]` entry with its own `model_provider`. Channels are routed to whichever agent should handle their traffic."
