#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md
msgid "The frontline agent handles every inbound message on Haiku. When it needs deeper reasoning, it calls the `delegate` tool with `agent = \"heavy\"`; because both agents share the `trusted` risk profile and that profile allows delegation, the heavier agent picks up the sub-task on Opus."
